Hi, Aliens! We are ET DAO which establish since 2021 Nov. We will build a SocialFi platform called ET Network based on Ethereum.

"Social to earn" is not a dream.
More information on our Official Website: https://etdao.org & Twitter: https://twitter.com/et_dao
